query: SELECT DISTINCT ac.user_id, COUNT(ac.id) as agent_count, (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM wallet_balance wb WHERE wb.user_id = ac.user_id) as wallet_count FROM agent_configs ac GROUP BY ac.user_id HAVING wallet_count = 0 LIMIT 10;
